pakiusap ko!

00:17:23.440 --> 00:17:23.880
Hindi ito matatapos, ha?

00:17:23.880 --> 00:17:24.920
-Umalis ka na!
-Maghintay!

00:17:24.920 --> 00:17:25.960
Inay!

00:17:25.960 --> 00:17:26.640
Tumabi ka!

00:17:28.580 --> 00:17:29.940
Ama!

00:17:32.040 --> 00:17:33.230
Malaking Ina!

00:17:33.730 --> 00:17:34.500
Malaking Ina!

00:17:34.520 --> 00:17:35.520
pakiusap ko.

00:17:35.540 --> 00:17:38.090
Mangyaring hayaang ilagay ang memorial tablet ng aking ina
sa ancestral hall.

00:17:38.090 --> 00:17:38.990
kaya mo ba?

00:17:39.160 --> 00:17:40.010
Hindi niya ito deserve.

00:17:40.010 --> 00:17:41.050
Hindi rin ikaw!

00:17:41.080 --> 00:17:41.810
Ibigay mo sa akin.

00:17:44.680 --> 00:17:45.280
Mangarap ka!

00:17:59.800 --> 00:18:00.600
Xi.

00:18:02.200 --> 00:18:03.540
Xi, tumayo ka muna.

00:18:03.760 --> 00:18:04.580
Anuman ito,

00:18:04.580 --> 00:18:06.440
talakayin ito ng maayos kay Ama.

00:18:07.560 --> 00:18:08.760
Walang kwentang babae ka!

00:18:10.000 --> 00:18:11.440
Sa Mansion ni Zhou,

00:18:11.460 --> 00:18:14.660
paano ka nangahas,
anak ng isang babae, kumilos nang walang pakundangan?

00:18:15.670 --> 00:18:17.870
Ama, pinakasalan mo ang nanay ko noon

00:18:19.360 --> 00:18:22.020
upang samantalahin ang
impluwensya ng pamilya Wang.

00:18:22.020 --> 00:18:23.620
Nang maglaon, bumagsak ang pamilya Wang.

00:18:24.000 --> 00:18:25.800
Tapos nagpakasal ka sa ibang babae.

00:18:25.880 --> 00:18:26.990
Xi.

00:18:27.280 --> 00:18:27.780
Itigil ang pakikipag-usap tungkol dito.

00:18:27.780 --> 00:18:29.940
Nakabuo ka ng koneksyon???
kasama ang pamilya Cui.

00:18:29.940 --> 00:18:31.940
At ngayon gusto mong gamitin

00:18:32.540 --> 00:18:35.980
pakikipagkaibigan ng panganay kong kapatid
sa Crown Prince

00:18:37.160 --> 00:18:39.970
upang hayaan siyang pakasalan ang iyong anak na babae
at bumuo ng isang koneksyon sa kanya.

00:18:39.970 --> 00:18:40.710
Ikaw...

00:18:41.400 --> 00:18:43.380
Ama, nakagawa ka ng isang detalyadong plano

00:18:43.380 --> 00:18:45.220
at naging napaka visionary???.

00:18:48.650 --> 00:18:51.340
Ngunit hindi mo ba kayang tiisin
ang isang maliit na tabletang pang-alaala?

00:18:51.360 --> 00:18:52.000
Ikaw...

00:18:52.030 --> 00:18:52.710
ako...

00:18:52.730 --> 00:18:55.450
Mukhang
hindi ka sinampal ng malakas.

00:18:55.580 --> 00:18:58.090
How dare you lantarang suwayin ang iyong ama?

00:18:58.680 --> 00:18:59.440
Mga bantay!

00:18:59.480 --> 00:19:00.160
Dito!

00:19:00.180 --> 00:19:01.940
Bugbugin siya ng husto!

00:19:02.020 --> 00:19:02.390
Oo!

00:19:02.410 --> 00:19:03.070
Inay.

00:19:06.250 --> 00:19:07.360
Inay.

00:19:15.370 --> 00:19:16.850
ano pa hinihintay mo

00:19:23.450 --> 00:19:24.490
Ang iyong ina

00:19:24.510 --> 00:19:26.980
hindi kailanman makapasok sa ancestral hall
ng Zhou's Mansion.

00:19:26.980 --> 00:19:27.090
Sinong may sabing gustong pumasok ng tita ko
sa ancestral hall ng Zhou's Mansion?

00:19:27.090 --> 00:19:28.980
